sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude/GPT/Llama)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS edge
    participant MCP as RHOAI MCP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAuth as K8s Auth APIs<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>8080/8443 HTTP(S)
    participant Planner as Planner Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over Agent,Planner: Flow 1: MCP Tool Call (Kubernetes Operation)

    Agent->>Route: MCP SSE/HTTP request<br/>Bearer Token (JWT/OAuth)
    Route->>MCP: Forward (TLS terminated)

    alt OIDC JWT Mode
        MCP->>OIDC: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration<br/>+ JWKS keys (HTTPS/443)
        OIDC-->>MCP: JWKS signing keys
        MCP->>MCP: Validate JWT signature & claims
    else OIDC TokenReview Mode
        MCP->>K8sAuth: POST TokenReview (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer SA Token
        K8sAuth-->>MCP: TokenReview response (user identity)
        MCP->>K8sAuth: GET User groups<br/>(user.openshift.io/v1)
        K8sAuth-->>MCP: User groups
    end

    MCP->>K8sAuth: POST SubjectAccessReview<br/>Check user permissions for tool
    K8sAuth-->>MCP: Allowed/Denied

    alt Tool Allowed
        MCP->>K8s: CRD Operation (HTTPS/443)<br/>Bearer Token + Impersonate-User headers
        K8s-->>MCP: CRD Response
        MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result (JSON)
        Route-->>Agent: Response (HTTPS/443)
    else Tool Denied
        MCP-->>Route: Tool not available for user
        Route-->>Agent: Filtered tool list
    end

    Note over Agent,Planner: Flow 2: Model Registry Query

    Agent->>Route: MCP tool: list_registered_models
    Route->>MCP: Forward request

    alt Direct Service Access
        MCP->>ModelReg: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/...<br/>HTTP/8080 or HTTPS/8443
        ModelReg-->>MCP: Model list (JSON)
    else Model Catalog API
        MCP->>ModelReg: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/...<br/>HTTP/8080 or HTTPS/8443
        ModelReg-->>MCP: Catalog models (JSON)
    end

    MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result
    Route-->>Agent: Model data

    Note over Agent,Planner: Flow 3: Planner Recommendation

    Agent->>Route: MCP tool: recommend_model_deployment
    Route->>MCP: Forward request

    MCP->>Planner: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP/8000 (in-cluster, no TLS)
    Planner-->>MCP: Extracted intent

    MCP->>Planner: POST /api/v1/recommend<br/>HTTP/8000 (in-cluster, no TLS)
    Planner-->>MCP: Deployment recommendation

    MCP-->>Route: MCP Tool Result (YAML config)
    Route-->>Agent: Recommendation

    Note over Agent,Planner: Flow 4: Dangerous Operation (Workflow Token)

    Agent->>Route: MCP tool: delete resource
    Route->>MCP: Forward request

    MCP->>MCP: Check read_only_mode gate
    MCP->>MCP: Check enable_dangerous_operations gate

    alt Operation Allowed
        MCP->>MCP: Generate HMAC-SHA256 workflow token
        MCP-->>Route: Confirmation required (token)
        Route-->>Agent: "Confirm deletion? Token: xxx"

        Agent->>Route: MCP tool: confirm_delete (token)
        Route->>MCP: Forward with token
        MCP->>MCP: Verify HMAC-SHA256 token
        MCP->>K8s: DELETE resource (HTTPS/443)
        K8s-->>MCP: Deleted
        MCP-->>Route: Deletion confirmed
        Route-->>Agent: Resource deleted
    else Read-Only Mode
        MCP-->>Route: Operation blocked (read-only)
        Route-->>Agent: Error: write operations disabled
    end
